commit 9d6d579f4482a9de792e125ce56f2f741c542079
Author: Marcus Better <marcus@better.se>
Date:   Thu Oct 9 20:39:39 2025 -0400

    Support IPv6 Unique Local Addresses
    
    This change correctly identifies ULAs with the fc00::/7 prefix, so
    that they can be assigned to endpoints and correctly matched to
    received packets.

